      <t>The present document defines a profile of Static Context Header Compression and fragmentation (SCHC) [RFC8724] for multi-radio devices or multi-network application. This profile can be used simultaneously over LoRaWAN, Sigfox, NB-IoT and any other technology that may use SCHC Fragmentation/Reassembly functionality.</t>
